title: Which Illuvinati Council nominee would you like to vote for?
body:
### What is the Illuvinati Council? 

The following blog posts outline the Illuvinati Council and why it is essential to establish it now while the protocol is in infancy. 

[preILV Airdrop](https://illuvium.medium.com/6-discord-pre-ilv-air-drop-the-power-of-an-ilv-token-ff4f1fdea0f8)
[ILV Council Purpose](https://illuvium.medium.com/7-establishing-the-illuvinati-governance-council-2cb0442ddaed)
[ILV Council Election Process](https://illuvium.medium.com/10-illuvinati-council-election-d8a8f2755d00)

### How are the votes weighted? 
Each wallet address will be allowed to vote for a single Candidate where the number of votes cast will be determined by the following formula:
C = N²
Where the cost C is measured in preILV and N represents the number of votes cast for that candidate.


### How to vote?

Choose an option below.

View additional information (including pitches) about the nominees [here](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ER93A9KuMeWv-M-u8-_vBAjOEm3dQohCTQwVcICowNM/edit#gid=0)
choices: Owen (WILL NOT ASK YOU FOR ETH)#2720
